  "texts": [
    "These embeddings are used to construct a gloss representation dictionary D(text i) = {emb_gloss j | j = 1, 2, …, n}, where emb_gloss j represents the j th gloss video embedding associated with text i.",
    "After learning all the glosses associated with text i, the Auslan learner records a video imitating these glosses.",
    "Similar to the Text-to-Gloss Search, we first embed the learner recorded video and then compute its similarity with all emb_gloss j.",
    "If the similarity with any gloss embedding exceeds 70%, we consider the gesture as correctly performed; otherwise, it is deemed incorrect.",
    "Limitations and future worksCurrently, our IACH APP is still in the Beta testing stage."
  ],
